{"tid":689424,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Devil May Cry 5》真續集等足10年E3公佈？大量情報指出！","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:08:18.000Z","uid":60286,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"281c9a5c7ff0e9430564709cdd470b52a1298076","tid":689424,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"重量級遊戲大作公開前一般都嚴謹保密、保持最大神秘感；不過Capcom動作鉅著《Devil May Cry》（鬼泣）的保密功夫就相當差勁，最近又有更多消息情報指出《Devil May Cry》最新作將於E3亮相，似乎大家可以期待10年不見的白髮但丁E3回歸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/132605_c3b033f84b1b4a3536b8644d3d6b0c50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F132605_c3b033f84b1b4a3536b8644d3d6b0c50.jpg&h=5cc5c28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果不計將舞台設在另一個平行時空的《DmC》，鬼泣系列的正傳作品《Devil May Cry 4》已經是2008年的遊戲，玩家們等但丁回歸已經等足10年。<br />\n<br />\n自從今年稍早時份Capcom在財務報告中表示「將會在今年公開兩款具份量的大作」時，很多人就已經推測會否是萬眾期待的《Devil May Cry》正式回歸。雖然Capcom從未正式公佈DMC的新作，但其實自去年開始已持續有大量情報流出（雖然大部份未能證實）。<br />\n<br />\n隨著E3漸近，陸續有更多《Devil May Cry 5》相關消息，首先是數天前在外國討論區reddit上流出了一張Sony在E3 2018上的發佈內容清單，上面寫有「Devil May Cry V」。而圖中《Death Stranding》、《The Last of Us: Part II》及《Spider-Man》這幾個數個項目已證實將於E3出現，如此看來這張圖或許有一定可信性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/132650_7e59aee04ccfdf5a62f99c641d00550d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F132650_7e59aee04ccfdf5a62f99c641d00550d.jpg&h=d3e0915b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，但丁的哥哥維吉爾（Vergil）的動作捕捉演員（motion capture actor）兼配音員Daniel Southworth在Facebook上貼出了自己和伊津野英昭（《Devil May Cry 2》設計師、《Devil May Cry》3和4總監）的合照，而貼文中有#E3的hashtag，只不知道是「手滑了一下」還是有意為之。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/132719_455e2fc5013d0ca6c5bc77d29eda974d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F132719_455e2fc5013d0ca6c5bc77d29eda974d.jpg&h=bf65966b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/132729_38b7d12336e9419dd94d676918055d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F132729_38b7d12336e9419dd94d676918055d89.jpg&h=b171a437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如此多證據之下，《Devil May Cry V》似乎已是事在必行，看來大家可以好好期待在E3中看到大家喜愛的但丁正式回歸了。"},{"pid":"5b8a9e2b119c97bdd08356632d1ce67c23ba7666","tid":689424,"uid":18350,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"淨係對from software新作有興趣"},{"pid":"d14dbf35a9e35b156ee05e71eadd728606c6f61f","tid":689424,"uid":165404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"第3集係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88fddaa5414b988f6197b6769413a5b0d042201","tid":689424,"uid":153442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"諗起之前DMC個吸毒樣就唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1292d414abe0592196603e4ff4b273dd49bb0bc","tid":689424,"uid":22643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14dbf35a9e35b156ee05e71eadd728606c6f61f","tid":689424,"uid":165404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"第3集係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"DANTE最型係第三集<br />\n第二集同 DMC都係黑歷史"},{"pid":"54d08956629295b9511a5bf2998fb38a1e798647","tid":689424,"uid":101219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1292d414abe0592196603e4ff4b273dd49bb0bc","tid":689424,"uid":22643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14dbf35a9e35b156ee05e71eadd728606c6f61f","tid":689424,"uid":165404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"第3集係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"